<h2> 부분 포함 insert </h2>
<div th:insert="~{basic/fragment/footer :: foot}" style="color: red"></div>

<h2> 부분 포함 replace </h2>
<div th:replace="~{basic/fragment/footer :: foot}" style="color: blue"></div>

<h2> 부분 포함 단순표현식 </h2>
<div th:insert="basic/fragment/footer :: foot" style="color: magenta"></div>

<h1> 파라미터 사용 </h1>
<div th:replace="~{basic/fragment/footer :: footParam ('데이터1', '데이터2')}" style="color: green"></div>
<div th:replace="basic/fragment/footer :: footParam ('데이터1', '데이터2')" style="color: cyan"></div>







